data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY 1/14/24 FROM 12pm til 2pm! :) Welcome to 989 Jeffrey Lane in the highly sought-after Neshaminy School District! This remarkable home offers a fantastic opportunity for anyone looking to experience the epitome of comfortable and luxurious living. Situated in an incredible neighborhood and boasting an array of desirable features, this property is sure to capture your heart.  With a pool (New pool pump put in this past Summer), jacuzzi, fish pond, fire pit, and a huge yard, this three bedroom and one & a half bath home provides ample space for both relaxation and entertainment! The two-car garage with additional loft storage up top and the five-car driveway ensure that parking will never be an issue for you or your guests. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an open concept living area that expands into the dining room and kitchen areas. The open concept design creates a seamless flow, offering versatility and multiple options for gathering with family and friends!  The office area provides a designated space for productivity and focus, while the mudroom offers convenience and organization for everyday living. It also features the included washer and dryer! The kitchen features granite countertops, an island with room for barstools, a giant garden window above the sink for the inner plant lover in you (not to mention a huge natural light plus!),  included stainless steel refrigerator, and so much more! The dining room and window feature bay windows that are perfect for decorating and also let in tons of natural light. The primary bedroom and one of the THREE living areas feature skylights, as well! That's right! There are three separate living areas in this home! One even features a complete wet bar and includes a beverage fridge and a deep freezer if the new buyer wants it!   The attic provides additional storage space, allowing you to keep your home clutter-free. Step outside and prepare to be amazed by the expansive yard, complete with a refreshing pool and a tranquil koi pond! Imagine spending sunny afternoons lounging by the poolside or enjoying the soothing sound of the water in your own private oasis!  For those seeking relaxation, the jacuzzi tub offers a luxurious retreat to unwind and rejuvenate. The fenced-in yard with a play area ensures privacy and safety for children and pets, allowing them to enjoy the outdoors with peace of mind. Additionally, the separate grilling area is perfect for hosting summer barbecues and creating lasting memories!  Situated on a quiet street, 989 Jeffrey Lane offers a serene and peaceful living environment, away from the hustle and bustle of the city. Yet, it remains conveniently close to nearby amenities, shopping centers, and recreational facilities, making it an ideal location for families and individuals alike.  Don't miss your chance to own this incredible home in Langhorne, PA. With its amazing school district, numerous living areas, office space, vanity-area, mudroom, open concept layout, attic, spacious fenced in yard with a pool, koi pond, jacuzzi tub,  play area, separate grilling area, and quiet street, this property truly has it all. Call today to schedule a viewing and make this dream home yours!!!!
